OL,3,CAddictive algorithms should be
OL,4,Cillegal, says inventor of the world
OL,5,Cwide web
OL,7,FTim Berners-Lee, inventor of the world
OL,8,Fwide web, says that addictive
OL,9,Falgorithms cause polarisation and
OL,10,Fshould be made illegal, but he does
OL,11,Fnot regret "opening Pandora's box"
OL,12,Fwith his invention.
OL,14,FHas there ever been an invention which
OL,15,Fchanged the course of human history as
OL,16,Fmuch as the world wide web?
