OL,7,FIt is now 36 years old, an integral
OL,8,Fpart of our daily lives, which has
OL,9,Fgrown far beyond what its British
OL,10,Fcreator Tim Berners-Lee might have
OL,11,Fimagined for it back in 1989.
OL,13,F"Well, it's been quite a rollercoaster
OL,14,Fjourney from the initial explosion of
OL,15,Fit," he said.
