OL,3,CAddictive algorithms should be
OL,4,Cillegal, says inventor of the world
OL,5,Cwide web
OL,7,FOne way they have been able to make
OL,8,Fthis much money is by using
OL,9,Falgorithms, which learn from our data
OL,10,Fto attract and keep our attention.
OL,12,FOne of the most effective ways to do
OL,13,Fthis is to elicit emotion - most often
OL,14,Fnegative emotions like rage.
OL,16,FTim Berners-Lee explains that social
OL,17,Fmedia networks employ deceptive
OL,18,Falgorithms which can feed you more and
OL,19,Fmore horrible stuff and essentially
OL,20,Fthen make money out of doing that.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
