OL,5,Cwide web
OL,7,FSo, is it possible to stop that from
OL,8,Fhappening?
OL,10,F"I think there's a lot of evidence
OL,11,Fthat polarisation in general is due to
OL,12,Fthe social media platforms," said
OL,13,FBerners-Lee.
