OL,3,CAddictive algorithms should be
OL,4,Cillegal, says inventor of the world
OL,5,Cwide web
OL,7,F"The systems are trained to keep
OL,8,Fpeople on the platform, so they're
OL,9,Frewarded when somebody stays on the
OL,10,Fplatform because of, for example, some
OL,11,Fhate speech. One of the things we
OL,12,Fcould do is we could outlaw that. We
OL,13,Fcould say you can make social media
OL,14,Fplatforms; the only thing you can't do
OL,15,Fis make them addictive."
OL,17,FBut is that really enforceable? "Well,
OL,18,Fyou have to tell them it's illegal,"
OL,19,Fhe said.
