OL,7,FOne of the most significant changes
OL,8,Fover the past 36 years is how much
OL,9,Fmore accessible the web has become.
OL,10,FGone are the days of dial-up internet
OL,11,Fat desktop computers, replaced instead
OL,12,Fby mobile phones - effectively,
OL,13,Fpowerful computers we carry around in
OL,14,Four pockets.
OL,16,FThere are fears that easy access to
OL,17,Fsocial media, in particular, is having
OL,18,Fa demonstrable effect on mental
OL,19,Fhealth, especially of young people.
