OL,4,Cillegal, says inventor of the world
OL,5,Cwide web
OL,7,FTim Berners-Lee still believes
OL,8,Fchildren should have access to the
OL,9,Fweb, but not be exposed to algorithms
OL,10,Fwhich hook them in.
OL,12,F"I'd like to see you able to buy a
OL,13,Fsmartphone with restricted access to
OL,14,Fthe addictive things for your kids,
OL,15,Fbut they have all the other good
OL,16,Fthings," he said. "They should have
OL,17,FWikipedia, they should have the
OL,18,Fability to call you up, and tell you
OL,19,Fwhen they're coming home. They should
OL,20,Fhave access to the web, just maybe not
OL,21,Fthe algorithms within social media."
