OL,7,FWhen asked whether he believes it
OL,8,Fshould be subject to something akin to
OL,9,Fthe Hippocratic Oath taken by doctors,
OL,10,Fhe said: "I think it's really
OL,11,Fimportant to have something like that.
OL,12,FYou can even legislate it."
OL,14,FDoes he regret inventing the web?
