OL,7,F"No, on balance. There are a lot of
OL,8,Fbad things. But on balance, there's so
OL,9,Fmuch good stuff. I think we need to
OL,10,Fkeep Pandora's box open. Just fix the
OL,11,Fpieces which are addictive. That is
OL,12,Fpossible because the people who make
OL,13,Faddictive systems, they know who they
OL,14,Fare."
